<p><b>Human Rights Council 
Thirtieth session 
</b></p>
<p>Agenda item 6 
</p>
<p><b>Universal periodic review 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Report of the Working Group on the Universal Periodic 
Review</b>*<b> 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Jamaica 
</b></p>
<p>  
</p>
