<p>119.34 <b>Investigate allegations of ill-treatment of children living in centres 
</b></p>
<p><b>and homes, and as appropriate, take all necessary corrective measures (Cabo 
</b></p>
<p><b>Verde); 
</b></p>
<p>119.35 <b>Take measures to prevent children from being economically exploited 
