</b></p>
<p><b>and informal sectors (Egypt); 
</b></p>
<p>119.36 <b>Strengthen measures to promote and protect the rights of the child, 
</b></p>
<p><b>including measures against sexual and labour exploitation (Japan); 
</b></p>
<p>119.37 <b>Take all necessary measures to protect women and children from 
</b></p>
