</b></p>
<p>119.39 <b>Adopt and implement a comprehensive strategy to prevent violence 
</b></p>
<p><b>against children (Slovenia); </b></p>


<p>119.40 <b>Conduct more effective campaigns, as well as necessary legal reforms, 
</b></p>
