</b></p>
<p><b>compensation and rehabilitation to the victims (Egypt); 
</b></p>
<p>119.43 <b>Continue to provide adequate resources to its anti-trafficking 
</b></p>
<p><b>programs (Philippines); 
</b></p>
<p>119.44 <b>Immediate elimination of the practice of incarcerating juvenile 
</b></p>
<p><b>offenders alongside adults (United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern 
</b></p>
<p><b>Ireland); 
</b></p>
<p>119.45 <b>Amend regulations related to arrest and detention by the Jamaica 
</b></p>
