</b></p>
<p>119.46 <b>Give INDECOM the power it needs to investigate criminal acts 
</b></p>
<p><b>committed by the Police (Australia); 
</b></p>
<p>119.47 <b>Adequately resource the Justice Reform Implementation Unit so that 
</b></p>
